Enter ATLYSS, a strange world thriving with creatures and critters. With the outside realm and dungeons deep ahead, there will be plenty of locations to explore and discover.

Fighter - The melee warrior class that deals devastating damage and threat.
Mystic - The caster class that evokes arcane magic to their advantage.
Bandit - The acrobatic mercenary class, experts of ranged weapons and quick melee weaponry.
- Play alone, or with Friends -
ATLYSS is made around net-play, but can also be played offline as well with no opportunities or features lost.
- Character Customization -
Make your character with five races to choose from, with color, head, and body sliders.
- Your character, saved locally -
All of your character progression data is saved locally and easily accessed within the game's data directory. Play a character in single-player, and join in later to a net-play session where you left off, and vice versa.

Party up with friends and take on quests to kill creatures, discover new locations, and help the last remaining safe haven of the world.
